Description:
Ballistic of the 120x570mm M829A2 APFSDS fired from tank gun M256 in the US.

This entry may be manipulated to yield the ballistics of the following rounds.
Projectile  Mass  Charge        Mass           Breech   Velocity
            (kg)                (kg)           Pressure (m/s)  (ft/s)
                                               (MPa)
-- United States of America Service Rounds (DU) --
M829A1      8.6   JA-2 19 perf  7.94 (0.8) kg  570      1570   5150  
M829A2      7.9   JA-2 19-perf  8.7  (0.8) kg  580      1680   5512

Gun parameters from ADA 18175 "A Propulsion System Comparison Study for the 120-mm Anti-Armor Cannon" (1987). M829A1 from TB 9-2350-320-14, projectile mass estimated from published performance. M829A2 follows GD-OTS product brochure.
